message.body: I'm interested in buying one of hunters skulls. I doubt it's i can afford one but thought I'd ask. Ryan's bday is coming up and I'm trying to buy him an awesome piece of art
I'll tell him you are interested! He's almost sold them all. There are like 4 left.
That would be such a good gift. I'll wrap it up with a bow.
I might just buy one for myself
He's gonna do other stuff this month. I like the skull, but the new editions will be much cooler.
Sweet. I was looking at his website. The skull is awesome but I like a lot of the other stuff too
Yeah they are all really sweet. He's doing a coyote skull
